text: Sara Rodriguez (born July 25, 1975) is an American registered nurse, health care executive, and Democratic politician who is the Lieutenant Governor of Wisconsin since 2023. She was a member of the Wisconsin State Assembly from 2021 to 2023. In November 2021, she announced her candidacy for Lieutenant Governor of Wisconsin in the 2022 election. She won the nomination in the August 2022 primary. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:State legislators of the United States Category:Lieutenant Governors of Wisconsin Category:Businesspeople from Milwaukee Category:Politicians from Milwaukee Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians
